nodes.text: The "Finhead Jedi" was a Jedi Master in the Jedi Order during the reign of the Galactic Republic. The Master was remembered in the form of a bronzium sculpture in the Jedi Archives.
The sculpture was an unused alien design and can be seen in the lower right of the Jedi Archives in Episode II.
